parameters: Demon...? If you're being cheeky, I'll crush you.
Wait... I... am not... a demon... Gug... Ugh...
Huh? So, you're really not a demon?

The city, which was destroyed by killing Faris of
the Golden City, was quickly taken over by demons.
Ugh... Where... am I... Who am I...

I apologize for being here for a long time...
Yes... I have become a demon...

It seems that you have defeated the Four Heavenly
Kings. Thanks to that, it seems like I've been
saved.
I'm glad you seem to be safe...

I am Faris, the Lolimon leader of the Golden City.
And you are?

I'm Konoha. I've been traveling around with Loli-
mon... Thanks to defeating Afurioz, I was able to
save you.

Not bad. We welcome you in the Golden City,
Konoha.
Faris... I'm going to crush you.
Wha...!? Aren't you a magical girl?!
I defeated the leader of the Golden City...
I defeated the leader of the Golden City...

The city was devastated and quickly fell under the
control of demons after killing Faris, the leader
of the Golden City.

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] Now, Faris...
Will you endure any more suffering? Can you handle
it? Hm? Tell me the secret of the sacred sword...

......Hehe... There's no way I would tell you... I
won't let anyone take over my town...

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] He's such a
stubborn guy... Even though we're on the verge of
defeat, he's a foolish loli leader.

I can tell, you're not very good at lying if you
think the golden city hasn't fallen yet... But
still, are you really a demon?

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] Ugh, how
insolent...! Hmph!

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0]... Such a
persistent person... Well, it's fine, I have
time...

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] Mmm!?
Konoha...! To think you've already sniffed me out!
Who...? Has someone come to see me?

So you're the real Faris! I'm glad. You're still
safe.

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] Interesting...
Magical girls, huh? It seems you're willing to go
to such lengths just to die...

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] I will grant
you eternal death... Let my power make you
realize.

How dare you deceive me and everyone else. I will
never forgive you.

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0], give it a
try!!!! Prepare yourself!!!!

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] Guhaa...!
You...! No way... This is... me...!

Four in the morning... Two in the afternoon...
None at night...

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] Ah... ah...
do... slave...
To the King of Death, Afuriozu...

I'm glad you're okay, even though that demon took
over you.
I put in so much effort...
Ah, you're here. Well, let's go home.

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] Hahahaha! Is
this all a magical girl can do? So weak!

\c[10]King of Death, Afuriozu\c[0] Now, I shall
make you spill the secret of the treasure sword...
With this, the golden city will become my
stronghold...!

Konoha, who was defeated, saw the golden city
quickly being taken over by demons.
